(133, 1, '2019-06-14 05:16:32', '2019-06-14 05:16:32', '<div>This green movement is a people driven voluntary exercise with heart full participation from youth across India. Every One is a tree leader who contributes to make our India the fruits bowl of the world.</div>\n<div> </div>\n<div>[smartslider3 slider=2]</div>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Credit of this whole project is to </strong><strong>Mother India.</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Every Indian who contributed to make our India the fruits bowl of the world is a LEADER here</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '17-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-14 05:16:32', '2019-06-14 05:16:32', '', 17, 'http://localhost/yfp/index.php/2019/06/14/17-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(134, 1, '2019-06-14 05:18:15', '2019-06-14 05:18:15', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To plan one lakh fruit bearing saplings every day &amp; nurture each of them with baby care.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Mission', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '51-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-14 05:18:15', '2019-06-14 05:18:15', '', 51, 'http://localhost/yfp/index.php/2019/06/14/51-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(135, 1, '2019-06-14 05:24:43', '2019-06-14 05:24:43', '<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>There were ancient times human life was revered by all other life forms for  compassion, kindness, generosity, love, affection, respect, obedience &amp; above all nature friendliness showered.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div> Life on earth was simply wonderful.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div> Nature used to be at its best with full of  freshness,  greenery,  fruits &amp;  vegetables. Every one enjoyed true  happiness.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div> Harmony &amp; peace were at zenith.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div> Health, longevity, fitness,  youthfulness,  beauty &amp; energy levels were all at optimum.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>All of a sudden, an alien dawned on earth by mistake &amp; experienced every thing beautiful about living. It went back and shared all the wonderful joys packed in its heart.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Since then,</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Jealousy, Greed, Cunningness, Foolishness, Cruelty, Selfishness, Carelessness, Fear, Doubt, Arrogance &amp; what not every army attempted to conquer but all were unsuccessful. They suffered humiliation and were forced to fly away.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Their desire to rule Earth dried up.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>But a very tiny bug managed to bite a human being and then quickly flew away.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Over a time, that bite became a  habit badly affecting all.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Every thing got opposite. Rest all is no secret. Thanks to our bitter day to day experiences.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>This dangerous habit that has been silently destroying us is not only about doing a wrong thing but also about not doing a right thing.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Just think-</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Do we spare time to plant &amp; nurture saplings?</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Don’t we mercilessly cut trees?</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>It’s high time that we take up plantation drive.</div>\n<div></div>', 'The Genesis - The Inspiration', '', 