(141, 1, '2019-06-14 05:55:05', '2019-06-14 05:55:05', '<div>This green movement is a people driven voluntary exercise with heart full participation from youth across India. Every One is a tree leader who contributes to make our India the fruits bowl of the world.</div>\n<div> </div>\n<div>[smartslider3 slider=2]</div>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Credit of this whole project is to </strong><strong>Mother India.</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Every Indian who contributed to make our India the fruits bowl of the world is a LEADER here</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>The Genesis - The Inspiration: </h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><em>LIFE ON EARTH WAS SIMPLY BEAUTIFUL</em></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":140} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://localhost/yfp/wp-content/uploads/sprout.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-140\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There were ancient times human life was revered by all other life forms for compassion, kindness, generosity, love, affection, respect, obedience &amp; above all nature friendliness showered.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><em>HARMONY AND PEACE WERE AT ZENITH</em></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">HEALTH<br> LONGEVITY<br> FITNESS<br> YOUTHFULNESS<br> BEAUTY<br> ENERGY LEVELS<br><strong> WERE ALL AT OPTIMUM</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All of a sudden, an alien dawned on earth by mistake &amp; experienced every thing beautiful about living. It went back and shared all the wonderful joys packed in its heart.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Since then, </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Jealousy, Greed, Cunningness, Foolishness, Cruelty, Selfishness, Carelessness, Fear, Doubt, Arrogance &amp; what not every army attempted to conquer but all were unsuccessful. They suffered humiliation and were forced to fly away. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p><strong>Their desire to rule Earth dried up</strong>.</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>But a very tiny bug managed to bite a human being and then quickly flew away.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Over a time, that bite became a habit badly affecting all.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Every thing got opposite. Rest all is no secret. Thanks to our bitter day to day experiences. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This dangerous habit that has been silently destroying us is not only about doing a wrong thing but also about not doing a right thing. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><em>Just think-</em></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><em>Do we spare time to plant &amp; nurture saplings?</em></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><em>Don’t we mercilessly cut trees? </em></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><em>It’s high time that we take up plantation drive. <br></em></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '17-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-14 05:55:05', '2019-06-14 05:55:05', '', 17, 'http://localhost/yfp/index.php/2019/06/14/17-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(142, 1, '2019-06-14 05:57:21', '2019-06-14 05:57:21', '{\n    \"twentysixteen::page_background_color\": {\n        \"value\": \"#b7d6a2\",\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2019-06-14 05:56:42\"\n    },\n    \"nav_menu_item[138]\": {\n        \"value\": false,\n        \"type\": \"nav_menu_item\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2019-06-14 05:57:21\"\n    }\n}', '', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'f5916274-1cab-42ed-a60f-a4aee021768e', '', '', '2019-06-14 05:57:21', '2019-06-14 05:57:21', '', 0, 'http://localhost/yfp/?p=142', 0, 'customize_changeset', '', 0),
(143, 1, '2019-06-14 06:02:12', '2019-06-14 06:02:12', '<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>To Make Nurturing Fruit Bearing Saplings A National Habit.<br></p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Our Top 5 Priorities: </h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1. Nurturing every sapling with utmost baby care.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> 2. Planting Fruit Bearing Saplings.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3. Planting in common areas.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>4. Planting One Lakh Saplings on all 365 days.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>5. Building green teams and making them self sustainable.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Vision', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '50-autosave-v1', '', '', '2019-06-14 06:02:12', '2019-06-14 06:02:12', '', 50, 'http://localhost/yfp/index.php/2019/06/14/50-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(144, 1, '2019-06-14 06:05:25', '2019-06-14 06:05:25', '<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>To Make Nurturing Fruit Bearing Saplings A National Habit.<br></p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Our Top 5 Priorities: </h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1. Nurturing every sapling with utmost baby care.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> 2. Planting Fruit Bearing Saplings.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3. Planting in common areas.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>4. Planting One Lakh Saplings on all 365 days.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>5. Building green teams and making them self sustainable.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are now going to the root of all problems. Imagine being gifted a basket of sweet mangoes! You relish and your family too. This is so with any fruit. This culture will gradually go deeper into our DNA with in 10 years ,not a long span.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p> Every one will find plenty of fruit trees every where. Enough for any one to eat. Every one gets healthy. Every one finds quality work to do. No crime. No insecurity. </p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><em>How will our society turn to be? Happy? </em></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>This is what we can accomplish by planting fruit bearing trees every where.<br>Keeping this big picture in mind, it is the need of the hour to plant fruit bearing saplings and nurture them for next 10 yrs. This mission has two major advantages: Economical &amp; Ecological. Our economy gets strength. Pollution levels will drastically go low helping us gain carbon credits. Temperatures particularly in summer will go below 25 degrees. We have to be committed for this cause at any cost. <br></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Vision', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '50-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-14 06:05:25', '2019-06-14 06:05:25', '', 50, 'http://localhost/yfp/index.php/2019/06/14/50-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(145, 1, '2019-06-14 06:05:53', '2019-06-14 06:05:53', '<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>To Make Nurturing Fruit Bearing Saplings A National Habit.<br></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Our Top 5 Priorities: </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1. Nurturing every sapling with utmost baby care.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> 2. Planting Fruit Bearing Saplings.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3. Planting in common areas.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>4. Planting One Lakh Saplings on all 365 days.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>5. Building green teams and making them self sustainable.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are now going to the root of all problems. Imagine being gifted a basket of sweet mangoes! You relish and your family too. This is so with any fruit. This culture will gradually go deeper into our DNA with in 10 years ,not a long span.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p> Every one will find plenty of fruit trees every where. Enough for any one to eat. Every one gets healthy. Every one finds quality work to do. No crime. No insecurity. </p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><em>How will our society turn to be? Happy? </em></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>This is what we can accomplish by planting fruit bearing trees every where.<br>Keeping this big picture in mind, it is the need of the hour to plant fruit bearing saplings and nurture them for next 10 yrs. This mission has two major advantages: Economical &amp; Ecological. Our economy gets strength. Pollution levels will drastically go low helping us gain carbon credits. Temperatures particularly in summer will go below 25 degrees. We have to be committed for this cause at any cost. <br></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Vision', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '50-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-14 06:05:53', '2019-06-14 06:05:53', '', 50, 'http://localhost/yfp/index.php/2019/06/14/50-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(146, 1, '2019-06-14 06:09:42', '2019-06-14 06:09:42', '<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>To plan one lakh fruit bearing saplings every day &amp; nurture each of them with baby care. </h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Execution Steps:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Building A Team: </strong>Every volunteer is encouraged to build his/ her team for a particular location. The role of a team leader is to facilitate all others in planting &amp; nurturing the saplings. The details of the existing teams of a particular place can be known from the District Head. <br><strong>Join A Team: </strong>If you want to join an existing Team, you are welcome to join. There is no role for politics/ ego / infighting. Every one is expected to enjoy being the part of a great movement. <br><strong>Identify Land: </strong> We prefer to plant saplings in common areas because once grown up, any one who is needy can pluck fruits &amp; eat. Identifying such land options is the collective duty of the team. How ever, the team leader will create a calendar for the activity. <br><strong>Resources: </strong>Every team has to be self sufficient in creating its own resources. No one is authorised to raise donations in cash or bank transfers. Any donation in kind is accepted. <br><strong>Name Every Sapling: </strong>Every sapling will have the name of its donor / care taker with a unique code just like Aadhar.  Every sapling will have a Care taker assigned who will take care of it till it becomes a tree. His/ her name will always be affixed on the tree in a visible uniform form. <br><strong>Website:</strong> The progress of our movement and the growth of the saplings will be updated on our website - www.youthforplants.in<br><strong>Tree Leaders Day: </strong>We will celebrate a particular day every year honouring the green warriors who selflessly lead this movement. After a decade, we may celebrate every day.<br><strong>Inauguration:</strong> We will Launch our “Mission One Lakh Saplings “ On 15th Aug2019.  <br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Mission', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '51-autosave-v1', '', '', '2019-06-14 06:09:42', '2019-06-14 06:09:42', '', 51, 'http://localhost/yfp/index.php/2019/06/14/51-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
